                     <interp inst="t18321018-184-person1637" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I bought two shells of the prisoner on the 20th of September, but I cannot swear to them.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18321018-184-person1638">
                  SOLOMON 
                  MOSS
               <interp inst="t18321018-184-person1638" type="surname" value="MOSS"></interp>
