            . I am a slopseller. The bed was sold to me by the prisoner for 1s.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18321018-184-person1639">
                  HENRY 
                  HYAM
               <interp inst="t18321018-184-person1639" type="surname" value="HYAM"></interp>
