                     <interp inst="t18321018-184-person1639" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I bought one shell and some other things of the prisoner - I gave the same shell to the officer.</p>
               <p>MRS. WILKINSON. The bed belonged to one of my lodgers - I know this bed; it has two or three holes in it- it has been in my care since before Christmas; I know these shells by some holes in them - they are our own; I have known the prisoner five years; I never knew him do any thing wrong before.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. It is my own bed, and was given to me by the husband. Witness. I believe his own bed is left behind.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 24.</p>
               <p>Recommended to Mercy by the Jury.</p>
